<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Q. I have an employee who does a good job, but all
of us have
</P>
<P>
   A4883 BC-SCI-RUSSIA-ANTARCTIC-660&AMP;ADD-NYT 937 18:49 U A
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIANS, FINANCIALLY PRESSED, SCALE BACK RESEARCH AT SOUTH POLE
</P>
<P>
   A4876 BC-GRAPHICS-BUDGET-NYT 363 18:39 U A
</P>
<P>
   A4857 BC-SPOT-BUDGET-BOS 398 18:28 U A
</P>
<P>
   For Release TUESDAY AMs, August 31, 1999
