Debra/Weydert/CORPHQ/NYTIMES. If unable to reach Ms. Weydert,
please call 800-444-0267, or fax us at 816-822-1444.)  
  
 (PLEASE NOTE: This article has been into the ``a'' domestic/general
news, ``f'' financial news and ``k'' commentary news files.)  
  
