<P>
   GARLIC (Clinton Corners, N.Y.) _ I had come to La Terre Garlic
Farm for a garlic refresher course. And I was about to learn what
those who shop at farmers' markets and grow their own already know:
some garlic is mellow, some pungent, some sweet, some astringent
and some with a bite that lasts and lasts. By Marian Burros.
