<P>
   HIKING IN YOSEMITE: I'm standing atop Half Dome, a sheer granite
cliff soaring impressively above this awesome park. I can think of
nothing but throwing up. My brother convinced me I could stop along
the way and read if I got tired. It was an empty promise. (Includes
3-column color photo hikers proceeding through the woods with a
llama, one 4-column color photo of hikers overlooking Half Dome in
Yosemite National Park and one color headline illustration with six
color mountains.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: YOSEMITE BOX: Tips for if you go hiking in Yosemite
National Park (Includes 1-column B&AMP;W map graphic of the park and
one 1-column color photo of hikers.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: DESTINATIONS: The legendary British Colonial Hotel, built
by Henry Flagler in 1899 and later rebuilt after a fire, is
reopening in September after massive renovations. (Includes
2-column color photo of The British Colonial Hotel)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS: Amtrak plans to put a customer-satisfaction
guarantee into effect by the end of the year. Passengers
dissatisfied with the service, food or other aspects of their trip
will be able to get a voucher with a value equal to the trip's
cost.
</P>
