   MUFOOT-SPORTS: DeVaughn Black, likely to be the starting
tailback for MU on Saturday, missed the entire '97 season because
of academic failures. He came back, without benefit of scholarship,
in '98, to earn his shot at one season in the sun as a senior. With
photos. &QL;
</P>
