<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Fort Worth Star-Telegram plans to move the following stories
for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of
Wednesday, Sept. 1, and thereafter. If you have any questions,
please call Lou Hudson, Paul Wagner, Tom Uhler or Jim Peipert on
