   LUCENT-BELLSOUTH _ BellSouth Mobility, Inc (BMI) and Lucent
Technologies have signed a three-year contract valued at up to $180
million for the expansion of BellSouth's wireless network in
Georgia and South Florida. Under the terms of the agreement, Lucent
will be the preferred vendor for all of BellSouth's wireless
equipment, software and service needs _ in both digital and analog
technology formats _ for BellSouth Mobility's territories in
Georgia and South Florida. (Kanell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
