<HEADLINE>
MONICA ASKS: WHO'S PROFITING FROM WHOM?
</HEADLINE>
  
 By LEAH GARCHIK  
 Copyright 1999 San Francisco Chronicle
<TEXT>
<P>
   During a three-day stint at Marie-Claire magazine that  &UR; Monica &LR; 
 &UR; Lewinsky  &LR; describes in a forthcoming issue, the former White House
intern refers to columnist  &UR; Maureen Dowd  &LR; as Moremean Dowdy.
