</P>
<P>
   YOSEMITE-SLAYINGS (San Francisco) _ Court records show that a
motel handyman, Cary Stayner, 38, has confessed to killing a
Yosemite National Park naturalist and three tourists in attacks
dating to mid-February. By JIM HERRON ZAMORA. (Already filed.)
