   Starring: Brendan Fraser, Sarah Jessica Parker, Alfred Molina.
</P>
<P>
   Plot: Dudley Do-Right always wanted to become a member of the
Royal Canadian Mounted Police (called ``Mounties'' because they
ride on horseback) when he grew up. And once that dream comes true,
