add new limits. Meanwhile, the families that have fished these
waters for generations say they're seeing their way of life dying
before their eyes. Kaminski says that the new 2,000 pound catch
limit on cod forces him to dump part of his load before returning
to the docks. (Mark Wilson/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
